reviewText: A good workout. Denise Austin gives you a good workout. You will love working out with her. She will make you feel like you can do every thing. And you will love it, even if it seems hard at times, she will make you feel as if it is a walk in the park. :-)
Video was just a described. Plays great in my vhs player. A fun workout keeps me motivated. Really like the upbeat 80's music in the background.

I'm not a doctor or a expert in exercices, I've been doing exercises with this video since 6 years ago, and when I did it during six months I get the best toning body I've ever have in my life since I get to the 30's.  So I want to continue doing exercices with it but now is almost imposible to get a new one.
